text: Ilkineyevo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Ilkineyevsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 327 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Ilkineyevo
